    "steam_appid": 3303870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/f8ce27104660fcd2532fef819eb6839c.avif?t=1771022508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras_big/f8ce27104660fcd2532fef819eb6839c.webp?t=1771022508 width=1560 height=181 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >化身地下城管理者，体验Roguelike 塔防 × 自动战斗的独特玩法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >白天迎击觊觎宝藏的「勇者」冒险队伍，夜晚扩建并强化你的地下城。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/f1b2d093f0621782d95fc5d8fce79b25.poster.avif?t=1771022508\" width=574 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/f1b2d093f0621782d95fc5d8fce79b25.webm?t=1771022508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/f1b2d093f0621782d95fc5d8fce79b25.mp4?t=1771022508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/8cb80c61c92c48da4293bf6690aba992.avif?t=1771022508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras_big/8cb80c61c92c48da4293bf6690aba992.webp?t=1771022508 width=1560 height=181 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造陷阱、部署仆从、施放法术，击退试图「解放」你宝库的勇者们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直面传奇级 Boss 的强大力量，检验你精心打造的构筑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/6092222f2d1edb2b41605d7982451384.poster.avif?t=1771022508\" width=674 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/6092222f2d1edb2b41605d7982451384.webm?t=1771022508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/6092222f2d1edb2b41605d7982451384.mp4?t=1771022508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/853ee45d3a8b8fb594c372beb65bfbb1.avif?t=1771022508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras_big/853ee45d3a8b8fb594c372beb65bfbb1.webp?t=1771022508 width=1560 height=181 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩充你的仆从劳动力，并将他们分配到地下城中的各项工作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开采珍贵矿石，为宝库赚取金币</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造并升级陷阱与建筑，迎接勇者的挑战</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部署仆从，应对下一波冒险者的进攻</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/54803f5154eb8c1f1d62b7dd1f1056f7.poster.avif?t=1771022508\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/54803f5154eb8c1f1d62b7dd1f1056f7.webm?t=1771022508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/54803f5154eb8c1f1d62b7dd1f1056f7.mp4?t=1771022508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/229a08cacfc9c9af4e8d732e813ab776.avif?t=1771022508\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras_big/229a08cacfc9c9af4e8d732e813ab776.webp?t=1771022508 width=1560 height=181 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过实用的天赋强化仆从，打造强力联动，守护你的黄金。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富多样的仆从、事件、远古魔典与建筑组合，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让每一次游玩都充满全新的挑战与策略选择！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/8a00d8e06270447c44d0e412cc5f4737.poster.avif?t=1771022508\" width=696 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/8a00d8e06270447c44d0e412cc5f4737.webm?t=1771022508\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303870/extras/8a00d8e06270447c44d0e412cc5f4737.mp4?t=1771022508\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
